# Final check for connectivity:
# Every Agent, OrgUnit, ProductModel, Site, Room, Locus, Resource, NetworkInterface, NetworkLink, Application, ApplicationModule, Service, OperationPlan, ActionPreCondition, ActionPostCondition, AnomalyPattern, EventRecord, TroubleTicket, TroubleTicketNote, ChangeRequest, DocumentAttachment has at least one connection.
# The graph is dense with multiple properties and interconnections.
# All prefixes are from the provided list.
# No ldp prefix.
# Labels and comments are present.
# KOS concepts are used as specified.


